text:
WWE: More Names Leaked For 2017 WWE Hall Of Fame Brandon Gnetz Start Slideshow Slide of 
It's nearly time for the WWE to release their inductees for the 2017 Hall of Fame. While it has yet to be confirmed, we've already had the names of the first two inductees released in Diamond Dallas Page and Rick Rude . 
Today, several other names of the 2017 class that are up for consideration have been leaked thanks to Wrestling Observer â€™s Dave Meltzer. They include a tag team, two stars who are still very involved in the action and a star from the rock n wrestling era. While nothing is set in stone, Meltzer is not one to speak of that which he does not know. 
if you don't mind SPOILERS, click through the slides to see which other legends may find their way into the class of 2017.
